HEADWORD: Overdraft
<hw>O"ver*draft`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Banking)</fld>
<def>The act of overdrawing; a draft in excess of the credit balance;
also, the amount or sum overdrawn.</def>⟦br⟧
